            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 1</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"img4\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img4', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Representation of a ruler measuring a line. The source code is available on the project’s GitHub (<htcite0>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Couting (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 1)</a>)</li><li>Rereading (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 1)</a>)</li><li>Understanding the Multiplication Table (2 and 3) (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 1)</a>)</li><li>Understanding the Multiplication Table (4 and 5) (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 1)</a>)</li><li>Understanding the Multiplication Table (8 and 9) (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 1)</a>)</li><li>Equality Levels (<a href=\"index.html?page=literature\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('literature','html', '', false); return false;\">Understanding Texts</a>)</li><li>Change of direction (Part I) (<a href=\"index.html?page=math_games\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('math_games','html', '', false); return false;\">Mathematical Games</a>)</li><li>Change of direction (Part II) (<a href=\"index.html?page=math_games\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('math_games','html', '', false); return false;\">Mathematical Games</a>)</li><li>Drawing to count (<a href=\"index.html?page=math_games\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('math_games','html', '', false); return false;\">Mathematical Games</a>)</li><li>1 + 1 = 2? (<a href=\"index.html?page=myths_believes\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('myths_believes','html', '', false); return false;\">Myths and Believes</a>)</li><li>Are addition and multiplication independent operations? (<a href=\"index.html?page=myths_believes\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('myths_believes','html', '', false); return false;\">Myths and Believes</a>)</li><li>Continuity (Universe)</li><li>Reality (Universe)</li><li>Simplicity vs. Complexity (Universe)</li></ul></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
